#: gui/dialogs.py:1208
msgid ""
"yt-dlp cookies file (cookies.txt) — only needed for age-restricted, private, "
"or members-only YouTube content. Installed browsers are detected "
"automatically; Firefox is recommended. Chrome, Edge, and Brave may fail on "
"Windows because their cookies can be encrypted in a way yt-dlp cannot read, "
"so a cookies.txt is the reliable fallback. LibreWolf uses Firefox-compatible "
"cookies. Chrome \"Nightly\" means Chrome Canary; Edge \"Nightly\" means Edge "
"Canary."
msgstr ""
"Archivo de cookies para yt-dlp (cookies.txt); solo es necesario para "
"contenido de YouTube restringido por edad, privado o exclusivo para "
"miembros. Los navegadores instalados se detectan automáticamente; se "
"recomienda Firefox. Chrome, Edge y Brave pueden fallar en Windows porque sus "
"cookies pueden cifrarse de una forma que yt-dlp no puede leer, por lo que un "
"cookies.txt es la alternativa confiable. LibreWolf usa cookies compatibles "
"con Firefox. \"Nightly\" en Chrome significa Chrome Canary; \"Nightly\" en "
"Edge significa Edge Canary."

